<title>ONWARD EVER ONWARD</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Krista'n sepaih hangsan leh thudik A deih,
 Galsatna phuol ah nang dingin mun a um;
 Khawvel gitloh do in, malam nawh zel un,
 Galzawh tieng van gam nawp kiemlo chang hitiu.

[V2]
 Pang un! Kross galmite haw,
 Lung laulo in, gingcha zing un;
 Pang un! Kross galmite haw,
 Suong un Lalpa, A thu ngai un,
 Galzawh masieh pang un!

[V3]
 2. Setan in ei nang, petmang dingin ei them,
 Mahleh ei lungsietpa vangin zo hitiu;
 Malai a galmi dang, galhatte haw chuh,
 Gimtheihna cheng zo in gam nuom a tung tau.

[V4]
 3. Hansanna chuh suoh in malam nawh hitiu,
 Isu en zingin, ngakin, ngen zing hitiu;
 I puonlap pei hitiu &quot;Krista namtin Lal&quot;
 Hossana sam leng Nuoizin gal zo tai tiu.</lyrics>
</song>